{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"44730-aatya-aani-mee","title":"आत्या आणि मी","description":"चुटकू त्याच्या आत्याबरोबर चालायला जाऊन येतो. परत आल्यावर त्याच्या खिशांमध्ये तऱ्हतऱ्हेच्या वस्तूंचा खजिना जमा झालेला असतो...शिवाय इकडच्या-तिकडच्या कहाण्यासुद्धा. एक आत्या आणि तिचा भाचा यांच्यातले भावबंध कसे उलगडतात, त्याची एका लहान मुलाच्या दृष्टिकोनातून सांगितलेली ही हृद्य गोष्ट. ","language":"Marathi","langCode":"mr","isRtl":false,"level":"2","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Meera Joshi"],"illustrators":["Rajiv Eipe"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Pratham Books","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/44730-aatya-aani-mee"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/117615/size3/2b5f77b28bb196dfb73d2b136890b5b0.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/117615/size6/2b5f77b28bb196dfb73d2b136890b5b0.jpg"},"audio":{"src":"https://storage.googleapis.com/story-weaver-e2e-production/stories/44730/audios/story/44730-aatya-aani-mee.mp3","cues":[[1,0,1.12],[2,1.12,1.8],[3,1.8,2.48],[4,2.48,2.92],[5,2.92,4.04],[6,4.04,4.44],[7,4.44,5.2],[8,5.2,5.6],[9,5.6,6.36],[10,6.36,6.84],[11,6.84,7.2],[12,7.2,9.68],[13,9.68,11.08],[14,11.08,11.36],[15,11.36,11.52],[16,11.52,12.08],[17,12.08,12.92],[18,12.92,13.48],[19,13.48,14.32],[20,14.32,14.72],[21,14.72,14.92],[22,14.92,15.52],[23,15.52,16.12],[24,16.12,16.64],[25,16.64,17.32],[26,17.32,17.6],[27,17.6,20.02],[28,20.02,21.8],[29,21.8,22.08],[30,22.08,22.96],[31,22.96,23.44],[32,23.44,24.42],[33,24.42,25.36],[34,25.36,25.72],[35,25.72,26.32],[36,26.32,27.48],[37,27.48,31.04],[38,31.04,32.2],[39,32.2,32.8],[40,32.8,33.48],[41,33.48,33.84],[42,33.84,34.6],[43,34.6,36],[44,36,37],[45,37,37.32],[46,37.32,38.24],[47,38.24,42.32],[48,42.32,43.28],[49,43.28,43.48],[50,43.48,44.28],[51,44